menu "FlightsAbove platform"

choice FLIGHTSABOVE_PLATFORM
    prompt "Hardware platform"
    default FLIGHTSABOVE_PLATFORM_SENSECAP
    help
        Select the hardware adapter used by the UI runtime. SenseCAP remains
        the tested default path.

config FLIGHTSABOVE_PLATFORM_SENSECAP
    bool "SenseCAP Indicator D1Pro"
    help
        Seeed SenseCAP Indicator D1Pro with the current RGB framebuffer and
        FT5x06 touch path.

config FLIGHTSABOVE_PLATFORM_LILYGO_T_DISPLAY_S3
    bool "LilyGo T-Display-S3 (reserved)"
    help
        Reserved target for the compact-wide LilyGo T-Display-S3 family.
        Selecting this target intentionally fails until the display, touch,
        backlight, and flush adapter are implemented.

config FLIGHTSABOVE_PLATFORM_ROUND_360
    bool "Generic round ESP32-S3 360x360 (reserved)"
    help
        Reserved target for the planned round display class. Selecting this
        target intentionally fails until the exact board/controller is
        confirmed and a real platform adapter is implemented.

endchoice

endmenu
